Rating: 4
We loved it! Disclaimer, I followed the suggestions: marinating overnight, adding to the marinade some sesame oil and on a whim some freshly chopped ginger. I ended up cooking the steak first in the marinade, then removed the steak so it wouldn't overcook and cooked the veggies in the sauce - onions and garlic first, and then the rest. Included celery AND broccoli. I'll definitely make this again in the same manner. Used boneless sirloin if anyone cares, it was outstanding!

